OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, BP has warned it has had to            
OL,6, "temporarily" close some of its petrol 
OL,7, stations due to a shortage of lorry    
OL,8, drivers.                               
OL,10,FThe oil firm said only "a handful" of  
OL,11,Fsites were affected by the fuel supply 
OL,12,Fissues due to a lack of unleaded and   
OL,13,Fdiesel fuel.                           
OL,15,FThere are around 1,200 BP branded      
OL,16,Fpetrol stations around the UK, of which
OL,17,F300 are operated by BP themselves.     
OL,19,FThe company said it was working hard to
OL,20,Faddress the issues.                    
